name: Tammy Baldwin
content: I have always supported legislation to allow Medicare to negotiate lower prescription drug prices. The House has passed #BuildBackBetter to do it, and the Senate should too. Let's have a vote and let everyone know where we stand on lower prescription drug costs for families.
text: always supported legislation allow medicare negotiate lower prescription drug prices house passed buildbackbetter senate lets vote let everyone know stand lower prescription drug costs families

name: Robert P. Casey, Jr.
content: Thanks to the American Rescue Plan, families who rely on home and community-based services are feeling the impact. It was an important first step, but we must do more to ensure millions of seniors and people with disabilities have access to these services across the Nation.
text: thanks american rescue plan families rely home communitybased services feeling impact important first step must ensure millions seniors people disabilities access services across nation

name: Suzan K. DelBene
content:
Prior auth needs reform. New @AmerMedicalAssn data shows that this antiquated practice delays care, worsens outcomes, & is a burden on seniors & their families. 

It's time to pass my bill that has bipartisan majority support in the House to deliver better care to seniors.
